{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Loudness Match (ZL)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 match the (momentary) loudness of current track (in_pin:main L/R) with the reference track (in_pin:aux L/R)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Loudness Measurement: the measurement used for calculating the volume\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Output: output from current track(main L/R) or reference track(aux L/R)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Lookbehind & Lookahead: the length of sliding momentary window behind/ahead\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Strength: the strength of matching, 0.0 indicates no matching, 1.0 indicates completely matching\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Threshold: if the (momentary) loudness of current track is less than the threshold, matching will not occur\sa180\par}
}
